rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I...have to stay here. This city is the only
home I have left.

rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0003
rows.name:
The restaurant is just scraping by,
but I still have a few regular customers.

rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0004
rows.name:
They don't seem to mind that
everything is so messed up and
they just keep coming back.

rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Sometimes it feels like a real nuisance!
But it gives me a reason to get out of
bed in the morning, so...

rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Maybe one day I'll even feel something
like hope again. Who knows, ha ha?

rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, sorry. You're trying to get on
your way and here I am chewing
your ear off.

rows.label: tlk70000030_04_msg0008
rows.name:
Prince Adel, Laura-sama, have a safe
journey and come back to us soon.
